{"tid":930660,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"<有片> 布殊生前服務犬   到國會瞻仰老友靈柩","createTime":"2018-12-06T12:50:09.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-06T19:42:49.000Z","uid":62257,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"6bcf997ee930cf6ba8c368d1fae8d8e52a5e3403","tid":930660,"uid":62257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-06T12:50:09.000Z","msg":"[url]<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=bexUQrCIjVs[/url\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DbexUQrCIjVs%5B%2Furl&d=BK1g1eN8jI%2B4p8cgbZaFdL%2BnoHux5cIPnxEj5ZZbdh4%3D&h=684658d4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=bexUQrCIjVs[/url</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20181205/58993229\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181205%2F58993229&d=BK1g1eN8jI%2B4p8cgbZaFdL%2BnoHux5cIPnxEj5ZZbdh4%3D&h=1af29897\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181205%2F58993229&h=d77ff208\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20181205/58993229</a><br />\n美國前總統布殊的靈柩周二停放在華盛頓國會圓形大廳（Capitol Rotunda），讓公眾瞻仰。在布殊人生最後歲月陪伴左右的服務犬「薩利」（Sully），被帶到布殊靈柩前，向這位老友記致敬。<br />\n陪伴布殊靈柩到華盛頓的薩利，由美國退伍軍人服務犬計劃一位經理牽到布殊靈柩旁。薩利一時仰望靈柩，一時伏在靈柩旁邊。與薩利一起到場的，還有《美國殘疾人法案》受惠者。該法案是布殊1990年任總統時簽署的。<br />\n布殊夫人芭芭拉4月逝世後，家人聯絡沃爾特里德國家軍事醫療中心（Walter Reed National Military Medical Center），希望有一隻服務犬陪伴布殊。美國退伍軍人服務犬計劃選了性格溫馴的2歲黃色拉布拉多犬薩利。<br />\n薩利不負所託，表現稱職。據說牠一聽到命令，就會將頭倚在布殊膝上。<br />\n薩利的名字取自2009年在紐約哈得遜河（Hudson River）緊急降落救了全機人的美國航空公司英雄機師薩倫伯格（Chesley Sullenberger）的暱稱。<br />\n布殊上周五逝世後，家人在網上發放薩利伏在布殊靈柩前的圖片，寫住「任務完成」的說明，令薩利舉世知名。<br />\n除了薩利，周二有數百人到國會大樓向布殊道別。除了前內閣成員及政要之外，也有普通市民。<br />\n參議院前多數黨領袖多爾（Bob Dole）坐輪椅到國會大樓，在布殊靈柩前站起敬禮。<br />\n中央情報局多位現任及前任局長亦有到場。布殊曾任中情局局長，亦是唯一當過總統的中情局前局長。"},{"pid":"e36017f2a5411813d4e347e445a19c9bbe813010","tid":930660,"uid":35870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-06T12:50:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a0374ccf16712d86f368fc0d3d2ad80b48d87cf","tid":930660,"uid":62257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-06T12:59:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3cf62be8a2f19257af489ae93742f73737016e6b","tid":930660,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-06T12:59:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> &lt;&mdash;"},{"pid":"44fa75d7faaf5aaf7c0809de425e833d2104200a","tid":930660,"uid":41116,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-06T13:00:19.000Z","msg":"good boi<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e071b2829387d2d640b652f38afab8040be7a77","tid":930660,"uid":50176,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-06T13:02:21.000Z","msg":"三六滾兩滾"},{"pid":"44884314d5d1bd51a1dd002c6aced42e0bdf1e17","tid":930660,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-06T13:04:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1613a3a84136a5b625e0199068aa2183a5b4878","tid":930660,"uid":13343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-06T14:25:33.000Z","msg":"我<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3634703f5cb4a4983250397ef7797e453d68c1e","tid":930660,"uid":62257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-06T19:42:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}